    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "At tonights council meeting the\nquestion of an agreement between\nthe city and the Washington Water\nPower company as to the Howard\nstreet bridge will be taken up.\n\n\nThe reports Of Engineer Bihler OF\nthe Washington Water Power COM\npany and City Engineer Mcintyre\nhave been filed with the city clerk\nby the board of public works.\n\n\nCity Engineer Mcintyre and Engi-\nneer Bihler agree in their reports on\nthe condition of the present struc-\nture and as to the solution to the\nproblem-which they state is the\nbuilding of an entirely new bridge."
    }
